      "content": "\u003cdiv class\u003d\"introduction img-head\"\u003e\r\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"header\"\u003e\r\n    \u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/png;base64,\u003d\"\r\n      alt\u003d\"App Icon\"\u003e\r\n    \u003ch3\u003eStore Segmentation\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n    \u003ch3\u003eStore Segmentation Analytical Application\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n  \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eOverview\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n      The Store Segmentation Analytical Application helps businesses understand different customer groups based on their buying habits. By identifying these distinct groups, businesses can create personalized strategies designed to improve customer engagement, boost sales, and drive overall growth.\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eInput\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Store Segmentation Data: Users input or provide access to data containing customer buying habits.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eOutput\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Data Profiling Insights: Displays null values per column, summary statistics, and feature distribution graphs.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Sales Performance Visualizations: Includes Month-wise Net Sales data and distribution of Total Invoices Month-wise.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eBenefits\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Personalized Marketing Strategies: Segment customers based on purchasing behavior to drive loyalty and increase sales.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Improved Product Assortment and Offers: Tailor offers and product selections based on segment preferences.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Optimized Resource Allocation: Efficiently allocate resources to different customer segments for higher profitability.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n  \u003ch4\u003eData Description\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"custom-table-container\"\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"custom-table-header\"\u003e\r\n      \u003ctable class\u003d\"custom-table\"\u003e\r\n        \u003cthead\u003e\r\n          \u003ctr\u003e\r\n            \u003cth\u003eField Name\u003c/th\u003e\r\n            \u003cth\u003eDescription\u003c/th\u003e\r\n          \u003c/tr\u003e\r\n        \u003c/thead\u003e\r\n      \u003c/table\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\r\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"custom-table-body\"\u003e\r\n      \u003ctable class\u003d\"custom-table\"\u003e\r\n        \u003ctbody\u003e\r\n          \u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003eCustomer_ID\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003eUnique identifier for each customer\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\r\n          \u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003eInvoice_Num\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003eUnique invoice number for each transaction\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\r\n          \u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003eSalesOrder_Num\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003eSales order reference number\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\r\n          \u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003eSalesOrder_Dt\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003eDate when the sales order was created\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\r\n          \u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003eSales_NetAmount\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003eNet amount of the sales transaction\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\r\n          \u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003eInvoice_Dt\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003eDate when the invoice was generated\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\r\n          \u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003eProduct_Cd\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003eProduct code identifier\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\r\n          \u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003eTransaction_Type\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003eType of transaction\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\r\n          \u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003eParent_Prd\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003eParent product category identifier\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\r\n          \u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003eProduct_Cd\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003eProduct code that links to the Customer-Invoice dataset\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\r\n        \u003c/tbody\u003e\r\n      \u003c/table\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n  \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003c/section\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e",
